    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Ma,",
        "I\u2019m writing with reference to the Bus No 5678 that plies the Lekki-V.I route. I have been encountering some issues as a result of the poor service in my area. I have to be at work for 8am every morning, therefore I have to leave with the 7: 00am bus. However the bus is at least 45 minutes late daily and that means I end up getting to work late. The usual response from the driver upon enquiry is that there are not enough buses to cover that area hence the delays.",
