        "I suggest that the company adds more buses to their fleet so that more than one bus can be allocated to each area. This would help reduce the persistent delays and unreliability that various areas including mine keep experiencing.",
        "Thank you in anticipation of your prompt action.",
        "Yours Faithfully,",
        "Mirabel Akpaka"
